<div class="container">
  <div class="faq">

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-sm-6">

        <h3>What is sororidade?</h3>
      </div>



      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="column2">
          <p>Sororidade tells the stories of women working in the tech industry in Lisbon.
            We want to inspire and empower other women to consider a career in tech, and help
          build a stronger community. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3>How are we telling <span class="samerow">womenâ€™s stories?</span></h3>
      </div>


      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="column2">
          <p>We ask women to talk about their experiences working in tech.
            We believe that storytelling is an important and effective tool to explore deeper
          issues that shape the tech scene for women. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">

        <h3>Who are we?</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="column2">
          <p>Luana and Sharon. We are two women working in tech in Lisbon
          who believe in the power of role models in shaping career choices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3>How can you take part?</h3>
      </div>


      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="column2">
          <p>Would you like to share your story? Or do you know another woman who is interested? Please contact us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
